 book exposes the global connections of a troubled region that must no longer be ignored.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 24. Mai 2022) 7aPOLITICAL SCIENCE / World / Asian.2bisacsh1 aHeathershaw, John, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertYale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2017z978311063898140uhttps://doi.org/10.12987/978030022209840uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780300222098423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9780300222098/original  a978-3-11-063898-1  Yale University Press Complete eBook-Package 2017b2017  aEBA_UCA_YUP  aGBV-deGruyter-alles